Quickstrike/Cyber Claw:




Quickstrike bolted out past Rampage and Tankor, and quickly turned a 
corner by the ship. He led the way there to Dinobot, so he thought. 
He stopped in his tracks, his body posed for battle. The Dinobot was 
still there, this time closer. 

He noticed something by his feet. It was a bot. And not just any bot. 
Rattrap. Quickstrike optics brightened with thoughts of revenge. His 
rounded mouth plate slipped into a grin. He looked back at the 
Dinobot, and noticed another thing different. This note was on the 
bot itself. It wasn't Dinobot.



Cyber Claw glared out cautiously out as a tiny young looking male ran 
out before her. He had a bizzare build, none she ever seen or dreamt 
of. 

She spoke: "Predacon, I come in peace. I am Cyber Claw. I want to 
join your group, forgiveness for my betrayal. I bring you a Maximal 
in hopes of a definate welcoming and trust." She picked up Rattrap 
with one hand. "Do you accept?"



Quickstrike blinked and turned his head to look at his two comrades. 
He turned his head back to Cyber Claw, and quickly said, "Yeah." 
Rattrap was what he really wanted.
